text: LA-10 is a constituency of Azad Kashmir Legislative Assembly which is currently represented by the Raja Muhammad Naseer of Pakistan Muslim League (N). It covers the area of Sehnsa Tehsil in Kotli District of Azad Kashmir, Pakistan. ==Election 2016== elections were held in this constituency on 21 July 2016.
